This UIView Categorie (Extend) will allow you to rotate a view easly 360°
Example:
---
[aView rotate360WithDuration:0.5 repeatCount:3 timingMode:i7Rotate360TimingModeLinear];
or
[aView rotate360WithDuration:2];
---

